		</Group>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="85" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成<span color="#ff9999">20%,20%,30%x3,50%,60%</span><span>伤害，强化前只施放2段，强化后施放至多5段。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="439" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人放下镰刀，从地面唤出2波成米字对的尖牙，两两咬合造成<span color="#ff4c4c">50%,12.5%</span><span>伤害，之后4对尖牙再次冒出，进行绞杀，造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" width="423" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人蓄势，立即突进进行收割，造成<span color="#ff9999">70%</span><span>伤害；若角色命中后站着不动，则强化后还会回扯一段距离，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人1.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1391" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人1.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1392" y="650">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人1.assets/Image_17.png')" x="720" y="874">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1200" width="443" height="250" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人施放有关于生命之契的技能后，会消耗自身<span color="#ffccbf">1.5%</span><span>生命值(生命值处于20%~11.5%消耗当前</span><span color="#ffbfbf">7.5%</span><span>生命值，生命值处于11.5%以下不会再消耗)，若该攻击命中玩家则恢复</span><span color="#ffccbf">3%</span><span>生命值；右侧</span><span color="#ff7272">红色</span><span>的伤害代表其会施加「生命之契」，该攻击命中生命之契下的玩家时，造成的伤害会提升</span><span color="#ffb299">150%</span><span>。<br/><br/>「生命之契」：消除生命之契后将使队伍中前台角色获得「赤叶」效果，角色进行重击将产生「血汐冲击」造成真实伤害，并消耗「赤叶」效果，该效果至多叠加1层。<br/>「血汐冲击」造成基于仆人</span><span color="#ffccbf">1.8%</span><span>生命值的真实伤害。<br/><br/>70%生命值以下进入强化状态期间，角色造成的伤害降低</span><span color="#ffb299">100%</span><span>(增伤区-1)；9%锁血转入二阶段。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人跃起，下落至玩家处并顺势收割，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害；强化后还将在近处额外挥动血翼，造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="436" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人打个响指，向全场施加<span textDecoration="underline">「生命之契」</span><span>，凝聚赤华，翻空振翼，展开万缕游丝，造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">70%</span><span>伤害，接着丝线交织迸裂，造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">100%</span><span>伤害。打断本技能施放则反噬仆人</span><span color="#ffccbf">11.2%</span><span>的生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">低于<span color="#ffccbf">70%</span><span>生命值后，仆人将进入强化状态：大幅减少所受伤害，为角色施加</span><span textDecoration="underline">「生命之契」</span><span>并允许施放「血潮赤宴」等更多的技能；生命之契的大小基于仆人</span><span color="#bfffff">10%</span><span>的攻击力，并且每2.5秒流失</span><span color="#bfffff">(1.25%HP+200)</span><span>的生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
