		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="439" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人进行3段攻击：两次使用旋转镰刀攻击，持续造成<span color="#ffbfbf">50%</span><span>伤害，之后转身化为鹰爪擒抓，造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">70%</span><span>伤害。强化前只施放1段，强化后施放全部。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人1.assets/Image_29.png')" x="719" y="649">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人1.assets/Image_30.png')" x="596" y="683" blendMode="normal">
